BARS

COMMENTS

TYPES
bool
int
string
float?
void

PRAGMAS
#version - string
The version string. Currently only "0.0.1" is supported.

#title - string
Inserts a title at the current position in the document. Note that the final
title provided is the default document name.

#subtitle - string
Not yet implemented.

#author - string
Inserts a right justified author name at the current position in the document.

#copyright - string
Inserts a copyright string at the end of the document. Any instances of "(C)"
or "(c)" in the string will be replaced will the copyright symbol (Unicode
#00a9). For the exact positioning of the copyright string, see #lock_copyright.

#label - string
Inserts the string verbatim as a label at the current position in the document.

#label_at - int int string
Inserts the string verbatim as a label at position (x, y) in the document.

#start - void
// TODO

#break - void
Inserts a small break in the document at the current position.

#include - void
Not yet implemented.

#comment_delim - string
Specify the delimiter for comments (default "!").

#background - string
Specify the background color as a hexadecmial string (default "#fff").

#color - string
Specify the color for everything drawn on the page as a hexadecimal string
(default "#000").

#draw_barlines - bool
Whether or not bar lines should be drawn.

#barline_padding - int
The amount of padding between barlines and the first chord in each bar (default
8).

#barline_spacing - int
The distance between lines in any barline with more than one line (ie; ending
barlines, repeat barlines, etc.). Default 1.

#barline_width - int
The width of single barlines (default 1).

#final_barline_width - int
The width of the wider line if final barlines and repeat barlines (default 2).

#margin_top - int
The margin at the top of the page (default 14).

#margin_right - int
The margin at the right of the page (default 22).

#margin_bottom - int
The margin at the bottom of the page (default 22).

#margin_left - int
The margin at the left of the page (default 25).

#text_font - string
The font used for all text (default "Arial").

#chord_font - string
The font used for all chords (default "ChordletType").

#chord_size - int
The size of all chords (default 14).

#label_size - int
The size of all labels (default 12).

#title_size - int
The size of all titles (default 20).

#subtitle_size - int
The size of all subtitles (default 14).

#author_size - int
The size of all authors (default 12).

#copyright_size - int
The size of the copyright string (default 8).

#first_offset - int
The size of the offset applied above the first system. This is the offset that
is also applied by #start. Default 4.

#system_offset - int
The distance between systems (default 14).

#label_offset - int
The offset applied underneath each label (default 10).

#break_size - int
The size of each break (default 10).

#lock_copyright - bool
When true the copyright string is locked to the bottom of the page. When false
the copyright string is placed directly after the end of the last element in
the document (default true).

#use_final_barline - bool
Whether or not to insert a final barline at the end of the last bar (default
true).

#stroke_width

#push_offset

#push_width

#push_height

#ring_x_offset

#ring_y_offset

#ring_x_margin

#ring_y_margin

#choke_offset

#choke_width

#choke_height

#pause_y_offset

#pause_line_radius

#pause_dot_radius



#key

#key_size

#key_offset

#key_padding

#key_box

#key_box_width

#tempo

#tempo_size

#tempo_break

#push
The following are not pushed: comment_delim, background_color, lock_copyright,
use_final_barline, key_box, title, subtitle, author, copyright, key,
title_size, subtitle_size, author_size, copyright_size, key_size, key_offset,
key_padding, key_box_width, first_line_offset

#pop
